{
  "texts": [
    "H1: Perceived usefulness (PU) predicts the attitude toward using ChatGPT.",
    "H2: Perceived usefulness (PU) predicts the intention to use ChatGPT.",
    "Perceived ease of use (PEU) is another critical factor in the TAM that impacts the user's intention to use technology (Davis, 1989).",
    "PEU refers to the degree to which the user perceives technology to be easy and free of effort.",
    "It is another fundamental determinant of user acceptance of technology (Teo, 2009)."
  ]
}